  "body": "## Feature Issue\r\n\r\nImplement `Community Request` notifications for Sender/Requester in Activity Center.\r\n\r\n### User Story\r\n\r\n> As a user\r\n> I want to see a notification in my Activity Center for the community I have requested to join\r\n> So that I keep track of the response to the request\r\n\r\n### Description\r\n\r\nThe user who requested to join a community will see/get a notification in Activity Center with the **Request Pending** state.\r\n\r\n![1 line](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/19339952/224400327-d2a5a8cf-3810-44f7-8ecb-4d008ba4c9df.png)\r\n\r\n\r\nIf the Community Manager `accepts` the request, the notification in Activity Center should be updated accordingly.\r\n\r\n![1 line](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/19339952/224397432-eb619015-806b-4911-8748-a654c361f189.png)\r\n\r\n\r\nIf the Community Manager `declines` the request or the request goes unattended/ignored, the notification in Activity Centre should be updated accordingly _after seven (7) days from the time of the request_.\r\n\r\n![1 line](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/19339952/224397349-fa475343-468b-4609-a2d7-4daa3fbae0a5.png)\r\n\r\n### Design\r\n\r\nThe community with the required membership approval flow are described in [Figma](https://www.figma.com/file/eDfxTa9IoaCMUy5cLTp0ys/Shell-for-Mobile?node-id=4537%3A515620&t=4P2KnrsUfTKRpy5G-1)\r\n\r\n\r\n### Developer Notes\r\n\r\nThis feature is a subset of a larger effort of community requests to join. Please refer to #15322 for the request to join flow updates.\r\n\r\n",
